sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant LoadBalancer as Load Balancer
    participant Server1 as Server 1
    participant Server2 as Server 2
    participant Database as Database

    User->>LoadBalancer: Request
    LoadBalancer->>Server1: Forward request
    Server1->>Database: Query data
    Database-->>Server1: Return data
    Server1-->>LoadBalancer: Response
    LoadBalancer-->>User: Response

    User->>LoadBalancer: Concurrent request
    LoadBalancer->>Server2: Forward request
    Server2->>Database: Query data
    Database-->>Server2: Return data
    Server2-->>LoadBalancer: Response
    LoadBalancer-->>User: Response